00:00:17.760 --> 00:00:19.760
regular pioneering for over six years.

00:00:20.640 --> 00:00:24.960
However, the reason we wanted to talk with them is that thus far,

00:00:25.359 --> 00:00:29.359
they have successfully countered Satan's attacks on their family.

00:00:30.239 --> 00:00:32.240
We'd like to hear how they accomplished this.

00:00:33.039 --> 00:00:36.479
First of all, Freddie, tell us a little bit about your family.

00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:39.439
You know, Lynette and I were raising the truth.

00:00:40.320 --> 00:00:42.399
However, we met and we felt in love.

00:00:43.119 --> 00:00:45.679
At that time, marriage was not for me.

00:00:45.679 --> 00:00:50.880
So we started a romantic relationship for two years before we started attending to the first

00:00:50.880 --> 00:00:54.960
meeting at the Kingdom Hall. So now after we started starting the Bible, we took two

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:58.079
studies per week and we knew that this is what the truth.

00:00:58.799 --> 00:01:02.159
But also, we learned that Jehovah held Jehovah's Seas in Marari.

00:01:02.719 --> 00:01:04.400
So we needed to do some changes.

00:01:05.439 --> 00:01:08.719
Lynette's parents won her to continue with her education.

00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:11.439
So we needed to change our behavior.

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:17.359
So two years after, we did change the changes.

00:01:17.359 --> 00:01:19.200
Number one, because we didn't love Jehovah.

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:23.120
And the two, because we loved what we were learning, it was worth it.

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:25.599
To follow the Bible principles.

00:01:26.159 --> 00:01:31.680
So two years later, we got married and we got baptized and then we got married.

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:32.480
Very good.

00:01:32.480 --> 00:01:36.000
So Lynette, you were raised without an knowledge of Jehovah God.

00:01:36.719 --> 00:01:41.280
What changes did you both have to make to ensure your own family would have a

00:01:41.280 --> 00:01:43.840
fine foundation and be successful?

00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:48.480
Well, prior to our baptism, Freddie had a serious drinking problem.

00:01:49.359 --> 00:01:53.760
And based on the way we were raised, there was a lot of jealousy going on.

00:01:54.239 --> 00:01:57.359
And I would say, like of confidence and trust in each other.

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:02.879
My Bible teachers, thankfully, suggested us to study the book,

00:02:02.879 --> 00:02:04.719
making your family life happy.

00:02:05.359 --> 00:02:08.000
And we ended up studying that book twice.

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:14.319
The publication and the Bible principles in it became the foundation of our wonderful marriage

00:02:14.319 --> 00:02:16.800
and the happy family we enjoyed today.

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:18.000
Very nice.

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:23.599
So Freddie, maybe you can tell us about your children and what they're doing with their lives now.

00:02:24.240 --> 00:02:26.159
We have two sons, Gabriel.

00:02:26.159 --> 00:02:27.120
He's the oldest one.

00:02:27.680 --> 00:02:30.400
He started regular pioneer where he was 14 years old.

00:02:31.199 --> 00:02:33.840
At 18, he was appointed as ministerial servant.

00:02:35.120 --> 00:02:39.520
22 years old, he's been working at the plumbing department at the Warwick construction

00:02:39.520 --> 00:02:40.479
for more than two years.

00:02:41.360 --> 00:02:43.280
Adrian, he's now 18 years old.

00:02:43.919 --> 00:02:46.960
And he also started regular pioneer when he was 14.

00:02:47.759 --> 00:02:51.360
Currently, he handled the account for the congregation and other privities as well.

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:58.319
Well, they both have had an early start in their theocratic careers that's commendable.

00:02:58.879 --> 00:03:00.319
I'm sure you're both proud of them.

00:03:01.520 --> 00:03:05.840
And we're confident that Jehovah, the one to whom every family owes its name,

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:09.680
is pleased that they're giving an answer to his taunter.

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:17.199
In addition to the family lifebook, what else contributed to the success your family has experienced?

00:03:17.199 --> 00:03:17.680
Lynette.

00:03:18.479 --> 00:03:24.159
The governing body has provided with so many publications with directions for families,

00:03:24.159 --> 00:03:26.080
of course, always in Jehovah's word.

00:03:27.039 --> 00:03:31.520
So we decided early on that whenever a question or an issue came up,

00:03:32.159 --> 00:03:35.120
we will not make any decision based on impulse.

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:37.759
Instead, we will research it in the publications.

00:03:38.719 --> 00:03:45.759
We pray to Jehovah for him to give us wisdom and we even pray for him to guide us to find

00:03:45.759 --> 00:03:49.439
the right time to talk to each other or to counsel the boys.

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:56.240
I have always heard that there were stages on the shelf life and personality development.

00:03:56.240 --> 00:03:59.360
So I research it in advance as to what to expect.

00:04:00.319 --> 00:04:07.039
In that way, we were not surprised when we saw changes in attitudes or ideas.

00:04:07.919 --> 00:04:12.560
And that helped us realize what needed to be addressed or corrected,

00:04:13.199 --> 00:04:16.800
as opposed to what was normal for that stage in the boys' life.

00:04:17.839 --> 00:04:18.800
Very practical.

00:04:19.360 --> 00:04:20.399
Freddie, what can you add?

00:04:21.199 --> 00:04:25.040
Over the years, I have learned how essential it is to become a good listener,

00:04:25.759 --> 00:04:26.879
also understanding.

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:30.720
I tell my family how much I love them every day because we never know

00:04:30.720 --> 00:04:32.160
when circumstances by change.

00:04:33.360 --> 00:04:35.680
Family worship is very important for us.

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:37.120
I know it's easy to put off.

00:04:37.519 --> 00:04:39.120
But the benefits are hard to meet.

00:04:40.319 --> 00:04:42.560
Well, before this arrangement started,

00:04:44.319 --> 00:04:47.519
as a family, we value the Bible study with a family.

00:04:48.240 --> 00:04:51.360
I learned that a fetus is six months.

