He can recognize family's voice.

00:04:55.680 --> 00:04:59.920
So I started a Bible study with my son when they were still under womb.

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:04.240
And continue to do so after that.

00:05:05.199 --> 00:05:09.120
I know that secular work and other activities can block

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:14.160
to the regular program, but we need to find that tendency.

00:05:14.160 --> 00:05:15.920
And we want to succeed in family worship.

00:05:16.480 --> 00:05:17.279
Very good.

00:05:17.279 --> 00:05:20.959
Well, it seems your efforts paid off when we consider how

00:05:20.959 --> 00:05:23.360
well your family's done spiritually.

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:26.639
In the close relationship you have with each other.

00:05:27.279 --> 00:05:30.879
Now, in that, it sounds as if the family is perfect.

00:05:32.879 --> 00:05:33.759
No challenges.

00:05:34.720 --> 00:05:35.600
Is that the case?

00:05:36.079 --> 00:05:37.120
No, not at all.

00:05:37.759 --> 00:05:43.600
First Corinthians 1013 says that Christians will face challenges that are common to them.

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:47.920
And we have faced the normal challenges that comes with race in a family.

00:05:50.079 --> 00:05:55.360
The same verse indicates that if we do things Jehovah's way,

00:05:56.160 --> 00:06:00.160
we may increase the opportunity for him to make the way out for us.

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:06.720
One unexpected challenge that has changed our family dynamics over the years now

00:06:07.759 --> 00:06:11.199
was when Freddie was diagnosed with cancer in 2012.

00:06:12.240 --> 00:06:15.600
The treatment was aggressive and took its toll on his health.

00:06:17.199 --> 00:06:18.959
Our whole lifestyle changed.

00:06:19.680 --> 00:06:24.319
We had to move out from our house to an apartment.

00:06:24.879 --> 00:06:32.399
We gave away our dogs' bike and we had to wash our expenses really closely to keep going.

00:06:34.480 --> 00:06:41.279
This could have put a lot of strain in our family and our marriage and in spirituality.

00:06:41.839 --> 00:06:46.959
But again, by praying to Jehovah constantly and applying by both principles,

00:06:47.759 --> 00:06:51.600
I can say my marriage and my family has never been better.

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:59.040
Spiritually, we kept our routine and we all stay in full-time service throughout the ordeal.

00:07:00.240 --> 00:07:02.720
The boys have cooperated very well.

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:05.519
They have offered to work to give us money.

00:07:06.399 --> 00:07:13.360
But we prefer for them to keep focused in the kingdom because we are confident that Jehovah

00:07:13.360 --> 00:07:15.519
will add on to the things we need.

00:07:16.560 --> 00:07:21.120
Freddie has been a great example for all of us because he pushes himself

00:07:21.600 --> 00:07:23.439
to keep his spirit to our routine.

00:07:24.399 --> 00:07:27.199
You never see him complaining or in a bad mood.

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:31.360
And that has been very inspiring for the rest of the family.

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:33.519
It's quite a story.

00:07:34.800 --> 00:07:40.800
You folks will certainly relate to the convention drama video that was advertised on our April program.

00:07:41.759 --> 00:07:45.279
Freddie, we're very sorry to hear about your physical condition.

00:07:46.160 --> 00:07:50.959
Are there any favorite scriptures that you've used to help keep you going,

00:07:50.959 --> 00:07:52.639
spiritually and stay strong?

00:07:53.519 --> 00:07:56.560
There are many of them, just to mention a few.

00:07:57.279 --> 00:08:03.279
Philippians chapter 4, 6 and 7 have been my life since 2012.

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:07.839
I have to pray to Jehovah constantly so he can give me the strength that I need

00:08:08.319 --> 00:08:10.800
to overcome my health.

00:08:11.680 --> 00:08:17.680
And also, Philippine says that he will give us peace of mind.

00:08:18.480 --> 00:08:24.879
In addition, he will safeguard our heart and that's something I've been seeing from Jehovah.

00:08:25.600 --> 00:08:33.360
Also, Isaiah 41, 10, stay that does not be anxious for I am your God.

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:38.879
Those words give me confidence that he will keep on helping us in these circumstances,

00:08:38.879 --> 00:08:41.120
of these different circumstances in our life.

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:43.200
I do understand them.

