So brother Maurice, she's been Proverbs 31 wife.

00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:02.559
A good wife for sure.

00:09:04.799 --> 00:09:08.559
Obviously, showing how much you love and respect each other, that's commendable.

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:11.600
And you're focused on being the best parents you could be.

00:09:11.600 --> 00:09:15.519
He's a good example for parents viewing the program at this time.

